210
0:08:49.26,000 --> 0:08:52,000
you know, your records with your doctor;

211
0:08:52.26,000 --> 0:08:54,000
that's a legitimate secret --

212
0:08:54.26,000 --> 0:08:56,000
but we deal with whistleblowers that are coming forward

213
0:08:56.26,000 --> 0:08:59,000
that are really sort of well-motivated.

214
0:08:59.26,000 --> 0:09:01,000
CA: So they are well-motivated.

215
0:09:01.26,000 --> 0:09:03,000
And what would you say to, for example,

216
0:09:03.26,000 --> 0:09:06,000
the, you know, the parent of someone

217
0:09:06.26,000 --> 0:09:09,000
whose son is out serving the U.S. military,

218
0:09:09.26,000 --> 0:09:11,000
and he says, "You know what,

219
0:09:11.26,000 --> 0:09:13,000
you've put up something that someone had an incentive to put out.

220
0:09:13.26,000 --> 0:09:15,000
It shows a U.S. soldier laughing

221
0:09:15.26,000 --> 0:09:17,000
at people dying.

222
0:09:17.26,000 --> 0:09:19,000
That gives the impression, has given the impression,

223
0:09:19.26,000 --> 0:09:21,000
to millions of people around the world

224
0:09:21.26,000 --> 0:09:23,000
that U.S. soldiers are inhuman people.

225
0:09:23.26,000 --> 0:09:25,000
Actually, they're not. My son isn't. How dare you?"

226
0:09:25.26,000 --> 0:09:27,000
What would you say to that?

