228
0:09:29.26,000 --> 0:09:31,000
But remember, the people in Baghdad,

229
0:09:31.26,000 --> 0:09:34,000
the people in Iraq, the people in Afghanistan --

230
0:09:34.26,000 --> 0:09:36,000
